:

1. *Ispalo* je da je on zakasnio na sastanak. (It turned out that he was late to the meeting.)
2. Nije se moglo znati da će se *ispasti* ovako. (It couldn't be known that it would turn out this way.)
3. Svi su se iznenadili kada je *ispalo* da je ona kriva. (Everyone was surprised when it turned out that she was guilty.)
4. On nije očekivao da će se *ispasti* da je ona nezainteresovana. (He didn't expect it to turn out that she was uninterested.)
5. Zbog njegovih postupaka *ispalo* je da je prevarila. (Because of his actions it turned out that she had cheated.)